list.abstract: west是一个英语单词，可以用作名词、形容词和副词，作名词时意为西、西部、西方，作形容词时意为在西方的、朝西的，作副词时意为向西、朝西、自西方、向西方。
west，谐音翻译为威斯， 是德国最著名的烟草公司．授权红塔集团，在国内生产销售威斯烟．AMERICAN BLEND意思是美国混合型。

yingyinNormal.en: Forgive me for using East and West kind of loosely.
yingyinNormal.zh: 原谅我很不严格地使用东方和西方。

yingyinNormal.en: Thanks, Frank. Welcome to the West Wing. Thank you, sir.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢谢 Frank，欢迎加入白宫。感谢您，总统先生。

yingyinNormal.en: Who's Adam West? Who's Adam West? Leonard, what do the two of you talk about after the coitus?
yingyinNormal.zh: 谁是亚当·韦斯特？！莱纳德，你们性交之后都聊些什么啊？

yingyinNormal.en: And it turns out in the end that the East isn't that far after all and the West, well the West, ain't so wild.
yingyinNormal.zh: 最后你会发现，东方并不是那么远，而西方人也不是那么疯狂的。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, I hope it's not a West Coast party, 'cause according to the man on the radio, a West Coast party don't stop.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我希望不是《西海岸派对》啊，因为根据电台里这首歌的歌词，西海岸派对永不停歇啊。

yingyinNormal.en: The West End in central London is a story in itself.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而伦敦中部的西区则又拥有另一个故事。

yingyinNormal.en: One of the busiest stations in the country is Beijing West.
yingyinNormal.zh: 中国最繁忙的火车站之一就是北京西站。

yingyinNormal.en: And right now, Raymond Tusk blows far too strong from the West.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而现在 Raymond Tusk的西风吹得实在太猛了。

yingyinNormal.en: I told them we were in West Virginia. What did you say? Kentucky.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我告诉她们我们在西弗吉尼亚。你说什么？肯塔基。

yingyinNormal.en: By who? Hm? The West? You don't understand Russia, Mr. President.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谁的赞誉，西方吗？你根本不了解俄罗斯，总统先生。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, it's Friday night. And you're going all the way to the West End.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，今晚是周五之夜,再加上你们要去西区旅途劳顿。

yingyinNormal.en: Hang on. How about now? We did it. We have the West Coast feed of HBO.
yingyinNormal.zh: 等等，现在如何？我们成功了。我们收到西海岸HBO电视台的信号了。

yingyinNormal.en: To our friends in the west, whose idea of war is a remote testing location.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我亲爱的西方朋友，你们以为战争只存在于遥远的荒漠。

yingyinNormal.en: We're leading the global fight to combat the Ebola outbreak in West Africa.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们领导着在西非战胜埃博拉疫情的全球性努力。

yingyinNormal.en: What about the flip side of that, the Chinese songs that have hit in the west?
yingyinNormal.zh: 但事情的另一面呢？传遍西方的中文歌曲？

yingyinNormal.en: That is so sad. No, what's sad is that you don't know Adam West was TV's Batman.
yingyinNormal.zh: 太伤感了。不，更伤感的是你居然不知道亚当·韦斯特是电视版蝙蝠侠的扮演者。

yingyinNormal.en: No! No one would mess with me. I told you she was too young for "West Side Story."
yingyinNormal.zh: 不行！没人会惹我的。我就说她太小，不适合看帮派主题的《西区故事》。

yingyinNormal.en: As an individual citizen based in south west of the country, I wanna speak it then.
yingyinNormal.zh: 作为一个生长在这个国家西南部的独立公民，我有话要说

yingyinNormal.en: So the United States will continue to help lead the global response in West Africa.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因此，美国将继续领导在西非的全球性努力。

yingyinNormal.en: America is leading the fight to contain and combat the Ebola epidemic in West Africa.
yingyinNormal.zh: 美国正在领导着控制并战胜西非埃博拉疫情的努力。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Chile (智利) is a long and beautiful country with ocean to the <highlight>west</highlight> and mountains to the east.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 智利是一个版图狭长而美丽的国家，西临大海，东临群山。

examination_example.sentence: Cowboys have lived and worked in the <highlight>west</highlight> and south.

examination_example.sentence: A big mirror is built into the wall of its <highlight>west</highlight> corridor.

examination_example.sentence: Limbo dancing is first from <highlight>West</highlight> Africa but today it is an important part of celebrations in the Caribbean.
examination_example.sentence_trans: Limbo舞最初起源于西非，但如今已成为加勒比地区庆祝活动的重要组成部分。

examination_example.sentence: In <highlight>West</highlight> Africa, animals provide humans with more than food.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在西非，动物为人类提供的不仅仅是食物。

examination_example.sentence: If you want to go to the zoo, you can walk <highlight>west</highlight> on the road.
